            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-description field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p>Tony Graham Recreation Complex&nbsp;– Kanata offers a wide selection of recreation programs for all ages including children's summer camps, preschool programs and fitness classes.</p>
<p>The complex includes recreation program space and two full-size arenas (Tom Flood Arena and Garry Burke Rink) with spectator seating. Ideal to rent for meetings, gatherings or social events. The Tony Graham Recreation Complex&nbsp;– Kanata is located in Walter Baker Park surrounded by various sports fields, park, a splash pad and toboggan hill.</p>
